You are calling
that piece of shit a plane?

4
00:01:05,315 --> 00:01:06,274
Yes, sir.

5
00:01:06,441 --> 00:01:08,317
It can fly over Mountain Everest, sir.

6
00:01:08,485 --> 00:01:09,777
It can fly over Mountain Everest?

7
00:01:10,445 --> 00:01:11,737
What? Are you kidding?

8
00:01:20,372 --> 00:01:21,205
Luosang.

9
00:01:21,373 --> 00:01:22,290
Come back here!

10
